felt like three years.

299
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:28,650
Jiu!

300
00:32:28,910 --> 00:32:29,860
Jiu!

301
00:32:31,170 --> 00:32:31,960
Jiu!

302
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,340
Jiu!

303
00:32:34,910 --> 00:32:36,100
Brother Zhuo.

304
00:32:36,130 --> 00:32:37,070
Brother Zhuo, is that you?

305
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:38,260
Brother Zhuo?

306
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:40,240
So noisy.

307
00:32:43,010 --> 00:32:43,930
Look closely.

308
00:32:45,390 --> 00:32:47,210
I'm not your Jiu.

309
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:49,490
I'm Li Lun.

310
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:53,740
I will make sure you die knowing exactly who killed you.

311
00:32:53,910 --> 00:32:56,230
See with your last look

312
00:32:56,290 --> 00:32:58,100
who killed you.

313
00:34:04,800 --> 00:34:06,660
I hated this bow so much back then.

314
00:34:08,560 --> 00:34:09,489
I never imagined

315
00:34:09,870 --> 00:34:10,790
that one day

316
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:12,330
I would risk my life

317
00:34:12,469 --> 00:34:14,199
fighting a demon to reclaim it.

318
00:34:29,250 --> 00:34:30,510
Thank you, Heng.

