00:34:46,810 --> 00:34:51,830
♫I only hope the snow comes a bit later♫

325
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:08,260
Mr. Zhuo!

326
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:51,250
Don't you hurt Brother Zhuo!

327
00:36:15,070 --> 00:36:16,010
Brother Zhuo!

328
00:36:57,170 --> 00:36:59,020
Don't waste your effort.

329
00:36:59,720 --> 00:37:02,940
My inner core has been inside Bai Jiu's body for many days.

330
00:37:02,970 --> 00:37:05,070
My soul has already solidified,

331
00:37:05,110 --> 00:37:07,310
making it much stronger than Bai Jiu's.

332
00:37:07,750 --> 00:37:10,250
His soul is nothing but a weak ant

333
00:37:10,430 --> 00:37:12,500
compared to mine,

334
00:37:12,530 --> 00:37:14,390
which can be easily crushed by me.

335
00:37:16,370 --> 00:37:19,690
After staying for the last few hours,

336
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:22,330
his soul

337
00:37:22,910 --> 00:37:25,570
will never come out again.

338
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:28,810
I'm too timid.

339
00:38:29,210 --> 00:38:30,040
But

340
00:38:30,070 --> 00:38:32,800
whenever I hear the bells on your braids ringing,

341
00:38:34,060 --> 00:38:35,370
I know

342
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:37,450
you're by my side.

343
00:38:38,750 --> 00:38:40,360
And I'll feel safe.

344
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:49,310
Are you scared?

345
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:51,410
With you

346
00:38:51,790 --> 00:38:53,910
and your powerful Cloud Light Sword here,

347
00:38:53,910 --> 00:38:55,390
I'm not that scared.

348
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,230
I'm sure it will be fine.

349
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:02,270
Mr. Zhuo!

350
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:07,300
Your body can't take any more!

351
00:40:07,340 --> 00:40:09,800
Don't consume any more of your Bingyi blood!

352
00:40:29,620 --> 00:40:32,160
Give Jiu back to me!

353
00:42:09,940 --> 00:42:10,740
Zhuo!

354
00:42:14,170 --> 00:42:14,970
Li Lun!

355
00:42:25,580 --> 00:42:26,650
Mr. Zhuo.

356
00:42:31,450 --> 00:42:32,980
You're really hard to kill.

357
00:42:34,040 --> 00:42:36,300
You ultimately managed to escape death.

358
00:42:36,560 --> 00:42:38,740
How could I possibly die before you?

359
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:40,370
Mr. Zhuo, wake up.

360
00:42:40,980 --> 00:42:43,040
I promise I won't argue with you anymore,

361
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:43,760
okay?

362
00:42:44,130 --> 00:42:44,940
Mr. Zhuo.

363
00:42:45,230 --> 00:42:46,490
Zhao Yuanzhou,

364
00:42:47,020 --> 00:42:48,950
I'm actually very grateful to you.

365
00:42:51,070 --> 00:42:53,790
If it weren't for you bringing this kid to me,

366
00:42:54,190 --> 00:42:56,720
how could I have obtained such a perfect body,

367
00:42:56,810 --> 00:42:59,720
so well-matched to my pagoda ghost form?

368
00:43:01,760 --> 00:43:04,620
You've finally done something that makes me happy.

369
00:43:05,870 --> 00:43:08,070
You cooperated with Wen Zongyu

370
00:43:08,490 --> 00:43:10,670
just for this body, didn't you?

371
00:43:11,200 --> 00:43:12,580
You know very well

372
00:43:13,180 --> 00:43:16,040
that once you break free from Baize Goddess's seal,

373
00:43:16,270 --> 00:43:19,020
your true form will quickly wither and die.

374
00:43:20,430 --> 00:43:22,150
You do know me well.

375
00:43:23,850 --> 00:43:25,250
But if anyone's to blame,

376
00:43:26,860 --> 00:43:28,860
it's Wen Zongyu for being ruthless.

377
00:43:29,850 --> 00:43:32,370
He even sacrificed his disciple.

378
00:43:32,960 --> 00:43:34,790
I've always told you

379
00:43:34,870 --> 00:43:36,330
that humans, though weak,

380
00:43:36,370 --> 00:43:38,190
are far more vicious

381
00:43:38,490 --> 00:43:39,890
than powerful demons.

382
00:43:41,270 --> 00:43:42,630
You never believed me.

383
00:43:44,240 --> 00:43:46,840
Wen Zongyu could even sacrifice his disciple.

384
00:43:46,980 --> 00:43:48,780
You're not his family or friend.

385
00:43:48,790 --> 00:43:50,530
How could you not see this?

386
00:43:52,020 --> 00:43:53,640
Of course, I can see this.

387
00:43:55,480 --> 00:43:56,830
We are just

388
00:43:58,270 --> 00:44:00,530
using each other to get what we each want.

389
00:44:01,910 --> 00:44:02,810
Li Lun,

390
00:44:04,660 --> 00:44:06,660
do you know his true purpose?

391
00:44:09,890 --> 00:44:11,530
The people of the world,

392
00:44:12,620 --> 00:44:14,270
bustling with activity,

393
00:44:15,080 --> 00:44:16,810
are driven by greed and desire.

394
00:44:18,290 --> 00:44:20,300
Wen Zongyu covets power

395
00:44:20,640 --> 00:44:22,700
and wants to destroy the Baize Token,

396
00:44:22,850 --> 00:44:24,550
allowing the demons of the Wilderness

397
00:44:24,550 --> 00:44:26,470
to enter the mortal world and create chaos.

398
00:44:26,470 --> 00:44:27,950
By doing so, he hopes to

399
00:44:27,970 --> 00:44:31,500
recreate the glory of Chongwu Camp's dominance over the world.

400
00:44:32,390 --> 00:44:33,550
However,

401
00:44:33,790 --> 00:44:35,610
Wen Zongyu is too naive.

402
00:44:36,630 --> 00:44:38,270
The naive one is you,

403
00:44:39,100 --> 00:44:39,910
Li Lun.

404
00:44:40,510 --> 00:44:42,970
You've lived for tens of thousands of years,

405
00:44:43,750 --> 00:44:47,000
but you're not even as wise as a ten-year-old child in the mortal world.

406
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:49,220
Wen Zongyu has been hunting monsters

407
00:44:49,460 --> 00:44:51,260
and secretly researching them,

408
00:44:51,580 --> 00:44:54,780
hoping to create demonized humans stronger than demons,

409
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:58,750
to eliminate all the demons in the world

410
00:44:59,690 --> 00:45:02,420
and turn the Wilderness into a barren wasteland.

411
00:45:02,440 --> 00:45:04,730
This is his true purpose.

412
00:45:06,550 --> 00:45:07,950
What did you say?

413
00:45:08,120 --> 00:45:09,200
Eight years ago,

414
00:45:10,740 --> 00:45:13,620
in the mortal world, the little demons

415
00:45:14,950 --> 00:45:18,210
we saw being tortured in the dungeon

416
00:45:18,510 --> 00:45:21,750
were captured and imprisoned by Wen Zongyu's men.

417
00:45:22,330 --> 00:45:25,860
That was the very reason we turned against each other back then.

418
00:45:26,770 --> 00:45:28,010
But now,

419
00:45:29,480 --> 00:45:31,850
you are helping the very culprit.

420
00:45:33,790 --> 00:45:34,590
Li Lun,

421
00:45:35,370 --> 00:45:37,400
you once swore an oath with blood

422
00:45:38,520 --> 00:45:40,280
to protect the Wilderness.

423
00:45:44,270 --> 00:45:45,630
Have you forgotten?

424
00:45:47,360 --> 00:45:48,400
No, I haven't.

425
00:45:49,840 --> 00:45:51,200
You're lying to me.

426
00:45:53,080 --> 00:45:54,480
You're lying to me again.

427
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:56,480
He's not lying.

428
00:45:58,200 --> 00:45:59,860
The one who's been lying to you

429
00:45:59,990 --> 00:46:01,710
is Wen Zongyu.

430
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:03,330
If you don't believe it,

431
00:46:04,930 --> 00:46:07,660
go to the secret chamber in Chongwu Camp to check.

432
00:46:08,110 --> 00:46:10,060
There are the answers you want.

